brought <i>me</i> the towel.

21:07.033 --> 21:09.867
She is such
a generous lover.

21:09.869 --> 21:11.369
Yeah.

21:11.371 --> 21:14.005
How did things end up
with you and the therapist?

21:17.743 --> 21:20.544
